        <h1>Daily Wage Calculator</h1>
        <p class="header-subtitle">
            <span class="citation" data-source="zendesk" data-ref="14243704039185">
                Centralized system for calculating daily wages across salary proration, leave encashment, and unpaid leave deductions
            </span>
