                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Improves payroll accuracy by eliminating calculation discrepancies across different scenarios
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-title">Technical Architecture</div>
                    <ul style="list-style-position: inside; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                            <span class="citation" data-source="validation" data-ref="plan_payroll_dwc_primary">
                                Centralized configuration accessible via Settings ‚Üí Payroll ‚Üí Daily Wage Calculation
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                            <span class="citation" data-source="validation" data-ref="plan_eos_config_primary">
                                Hierarchical override system where payroll settings control EOS and leave policy calculations
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">
                            <span class="citation" data-source="validation" data-ref="plan_leaves_unpaid_policy">
                                Policy-level fields disabled when global daily wage calculation is configured
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="citation" data-source="zendesk" data-ref="14154746403601">
                                Integrates with payroll system to automatically reflect deductions in payroll table
                            </span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
