                <strong>Important:</strong> 
                <span class="citation" data-source="zendesk" data-ref="14243760419089">
                    Changes to daily wage calculation settings will affect all active (unpaid) amounts in the payroll table. When payroll month is open, existing prorated salary transactions must be rejected and resaved after configuration changes.
                </span>
            </div>
