                            Settings ‚Üí Payroll ‚Üí End of Service Eligibility ‚Üí Configure button
                        </span>
                    </p>
                    <span class="tag tag-primary">Secondary Path</span>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-title">Unpaid Leave Access</div>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing);">
                        <span class="citation" data-source="validation" data-ref="check_leaves_nav_unpaid">
